          "body": "rājovāca bhagavan asmatkulasthitiriyaṃ ya eva kanyābhir ucito 'bhijavānvarastasmai kanyā pradīyate bhagavadyācñā cāsmanmanorathānāmapyatigocajaravartinī kathamapyeṣā saṃjātā tadevamupasthite na vidmaḥ kiṃ kurma ityetanmayācintyata ityabhihite ca tena bhūbhujā muniracintayat //"
